-- Corpbank's majority holder says works for bank rehabilitation
-- By Angel Krasimirov
-- Mon Aug 25, 2014 05:53AM EDT
-- None



BUCHAREST, Aug 25 (Reuters) - Troubled Bulgaria Corporate Commericial Bank's (Corpbank) <6C9.BB> majority owner said on Monday he was working hard to restructure the lender jointly with Oman's sovereign wealth fund and other interested investors.

